msgid ""
"Current settings defined in the :guilabel:`DXF Export` dialog may be stored "
"in an XML file for reusing them in other sessions. For this, the "
":guilabel:`Settings` combo box has two options: :guilabel:`Load Settings "
"from File...` and :guilabel:`Save Settings to File...`."
